Our bathroom is always available to anyone who needs it,  just mention to the front desk something like "Sorry, I know your bathroom is clean, I'll just be a second" and they will leave you be. Just a heads up: when anyone comes in the front desk staff stands up and ask if you have a reservation. It's literally in our job description.
